{
  "texts": [
    "The proposed neural network model combines the features of both CNN and LSTM layers.",
    "CNNs have excellent feature extraction capabilities, making them useful in a variety of applications.",
    "Through convolution and pooling layers, CNN efficiently extracts meaningful features from raw data.",
    "CNN is a kind of feed-forward deep learning model that offers parameter sharing and sparse interaction characteristics while differing from a multi-layered deep neural network that is fully connected (each input neuron being interconnected with each output neuron).",
    "In other words, under CNN, feature extraction is enhanced while the connection's complexity is reduced."
  ]
}